  "title": "Technician (Maintenance) – Automotive / Motor Vehicle / Car",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2000 to $3000 + AWS + VB + OT</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Upper Thomson</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: 5.5 days</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 9.00am - 6.00pm / 9.00am - 2.00pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Carry out maintenance servicing and repair of motor vehicles</strong></li>\n  <li>Conduct diagnostic checks, troubleshooting, automatic transmission and engine overhaul</li>\n  <li>Perform quality checks and road tests on vehicles</li>\n  <li>Liaise with Service Advisors on service/repairs-related matters</li>\n  <li>Provide support to customer service and workshop</li>\n  <li>Maintain facilities and equipment of the workshop</li>\n  <li>Any other or ad-hoc assignments by the Workshop Manager Requirements</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 - 3 years of relevant experience in automotive industry</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of various makes and models of vehicles is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
